# Treat embedded yt-dlp binaries as binary so Windows checkouts don't
# CRLF-mangle them and Git's binary-diff stays compact. The committed
# files are 1-byte placeholders (real binaries are fetched into these
# paths by tools/fetch-ytdlp.sh before `wails build`), but tagging
# them now means we're robust even if a real binary ever gets
# committed by accident.
bundled/yt-dlp_macos binary
bundled/yt-dlp.exe   binary
bundled/yt-dlp_linux binary
